line_1: To mock the frantick Rage of cruel Saul;
line_2: And strike the useless Jav'lin to the Wall.

line_1: Is this, alas, the End of mighty Saul?
line_2: But why, amongst the Heathen doom'd to fall?

line_1: Driv'n out an exile from the face of Saul,
line_2: See Judah's promised king, bereft of all,

line_1: Thy arm unseen eluded cruel Saul,
line_2: And struck the useless Javelin to the Wall.
